# API endpoints & Swagger

Follow the endpoint template in `docs/API_SPECIFICATION.md`. Skills: `new-endpoint`, `nestjs-swagger`.

## Same-task requirements

When adding or changing a route:

1. Document it in `docs/API_SPECIFICATION.md`.
2. Add/update Swagger: `@ApiTags`, `@ApiOperation`, `@ApiResponse` on the controller; `@ApiProperty` on DTOs.
3. Controllers return bare data (global envelope handles wrapping).

## Pricing

Server is source of truth for all money. Never trust client-submitted cart totals, discounts, shipping fees, or order totals — compute from the database.

## New endpoints

Prefer the `new-endpoint` skill so DTO, controller, service, and API-spec entry stay aligned.
